rows.label: qst202018_msg003
rows.name: How were the two of them doing?

rows.label: qst202018_msg004
rows.name: They seemed to be doing well.

rows.label: qst202018_msg005
rows.name: We properly delivered the golden bracers.

rows.label: qst202018_msg006
rows.name: I see. That's a relief to hear.

rows.label: qst202018_msg007
rows.name: Have Artus and Noelia grown up a lot?

rows.label: qst202018_msg009
rows.name:
Oh right, they gave us something 
for Musubi and you, Old Man.

rows.label: qst202018_msg011
rows.name: And they said they'll come visit sometime.

rows.label: qst202018_msg012
rows.name:
Oh, that would be wonderful.
I'm getting excited already!

rows.label: qst202018_msg013
rows.name:
I haven't seen them since they got married. 
I wonder how many years it's been...

rows.label: qst202018_msg014
rows.name:
I can't wait to see them! 
This is really exciting, isn't it, Dofusei-san?

rows.label: qst202018_msg016
rows.name:
So they're doing well, are they? 
They didn't need to go to all this trouble though...

rows.label: qst202018_msg018
rows.name:
Of course he is! His family who live 
far away are coming to visit after all.
